              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34727651/" class="">第294页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3047846/" class=" " title="redenemy">redenemy</a>
                (专啃毒草 越大越好)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34727651">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">共和精神和共和制度只能产生于商业民族！</span>
